          "question": "<p><a name=\"19829\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>In how many ways can the letters of the word \\( \\text{ABACUS} \\) be rearranged such that the vowels always appear together?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>Combinatory: TIFR CSE 2011 | Part A | Question: 2</b></p>",
